dct_title_s: Meiji kaisei Tōkyō zenzu fusai Yokohama shigaizu; Miyagi Keiten.
dct_description_sm: Mounted cover title. Copperplate print. In Japanese. Oriented with north to the upper right. 6 sheets joined. Relief shown by hachures. Includes address chart of banks, inset of Yokohama and legend. 1 map: col.; 83 x 96 cm., folded in cover 19 x 13 cm.
dct_rights_sm: This map is in the public domain.
